title: How can I fix issue with update version 11?
content:
Since version 11 updated on my phone, when I connect my phone via bluetooth to my car I can't see the song details and I can't change up or down though the songs. This worked prior. 
I have reset my phone, I have downloaded and installed the apps which are not working, I have disconnected and reconnected via bluetooth my phone to my car. 
Can I uninstalled version 11 or can this be sorted? 
Also does this happens to the google pixel 5? 

Please could someone help
category: Connectivity, Network, Bluetooth, Google Pixel 3 XL
